Description:
    Create component directory and initialization file

Options:
    [options] are supported to be passed in the sequence of <name>=<value> format.
    <name> should be one of the followings -

    license     : license name such as GPL, LGPL, MIT, ... etc (default: MIT)
    url         : support url  (default: NA)
    author      : author name  (default: current user)

Example:
    ./script/generate wj_component blog
    ./script/generate wj_component blog license=MIT
    ./script/generate wj_component blog author=yssk22 url=http://trac.webjourney.org/components/blog
